Spanish Paella & Wine Gift Set
List.Description:
This gift set includes everything you need to make paella plus Cortijo Tinto! It includes a traditional steel paella pan, imported saffron, pimento, sofrito sauce, olives, and paella rice. The Cortijo Tinto complements the flavors of Spanish Paella.

Wine Gift Includes:

  • Don Sancho Londono Cortijo Tinto:
    This Cortijo Tinto shows a terrific array of cherry and black raspberry aromas with earth notes before a surprisingly rich, full wine with loads of savory fruit and a long, pure finish.

  • Paella Pan 13in
  • Paella Rice 2.2 lbs.
  • Saffron 1 gram
  • Sweet Smoked Pimenton 2.6 oz
  • Sofrito Sauce 12.3 oz
  • Spanish Manzanilla Olives 2 oz

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.
